06:12.004 --> 06:13.541
- It's important.

06:15.541 --> 06:16.908
- What is it then?

06:16.908 --> 06:18.543
(lightly crying)

06:18.543 --> 06:19.848
- I, I'm pregnant.

06:23.848 --> 06:25.050
(light dramatic music)

06:25.050 --> 06:25.851
- What?

06:26.851 --> 06:28.220
- I'm pregnant.

06:28.220 --> 06:32.156
- You're 15 years old,
what were you thinking?

06:32.156 --> 06:33.992
- I'm sorry.

06:33.992 --> 06:35.961
- Do you know what this
will do to my business?

06:35.961 --> 06:37.495
What will people say
when they find out

06:37.495 --> 06:40.732
I have a 15 year old
pregnant daughter?

06:40.732 --> 06:42.935
- Daddy, I'm sorry.

06:42.935 --> 06:45.670
- You know, you're
just like your mother.

06:45.670 --> 06:47.906
- [Jade] Daddy, please.

06:47.906 --> 06:49.208
- I'm done with you.

06:49.208 --> 06:52.011
As far as I'm concerned,
I have no daughter.

06:53.011 --> 06:57.615
- You can't make me leave.
- Get out of here.

06:57.615 --> 06:59.086
(crying)

07:02.086 --> 07:03.622
- Thank you.

07:03.622 --> 07:05.223
May God bless you.

07:05.223 --> 07:06.858
How are you guys?
- Hi, very well.

07:06.858 --> 07:08.526
- You look awfully
pretty this day.

07:08.526 --> 07:09.028
- [Faith] Thank
you, Pastor Mark.

07:10.028 --> 07:11.196
- You guys been doing well?

07:11.196 --> 07:12.898
- Good, Pastor.

07:12.898 --> 07:14.500
