over to dinner next week.

07:14.500 --> 07:15.968
- Only if you're cooking
that fried chicken.

07:15.968 --> 07:17.101
- Just the way you like it.

07:17.101 --> 07:18.103
- We'll be there.

07:18.103 --> 07:19.238
- Alright.

07:19.238 --> 07:21.610
- Good to see you guys.
- Bye-bye.

07:25.610 --> 07:27.713
- That sure was a nice
service today, wasn't it?

07:27.713 --> 07:29.047
- It sure was.

07:29.047 --> 07:30.016
Hey, why don't you guys
go ahead and wash up

07:31.016 --> 07:33.151
while I get lunch ready, okay?

07:33.151 --> 07:34.754
- Yes, ma'am.

07:35.754 --> 07:36.690
Let's pray.

07:38.690 --> 07:41.593
God, our Father,
Lord and Savior,

07:41.593 --> 07:43.595
