your great service.

07:49.901 --> 07:52.603
In your holy name,
we pray, Amen.

07:52.603 --> 07:53.040
- Amen.
- Amen.

07:56.040 --> 07:58.976
Oh, happy anniversary,
by the way.

07:58.976 --> 08:00.978
- Thanks.
- Yeah, thanks sweetheart.

08:00.978 --> 08:02.581
