14:10.548 --> 14:13.224
(light dramatic music)

14:19.224 --> 14:22.365
(knocking on door)

14:27.365 --> 14:29.301
- Yes, can I help you?

14:29.301 --> 14:32.269
- [Jade] Can I speak
to Chris, please?

14:32.269 --> 14:36.010
- Chris, there's some
girl at the door for you.

14:40.010 --> 14:41.980
You know I don't like
people here this late.

14:41.980 --> 14:44.182
Just take care of this.

14:44.182 --> 14:45.351
- Alright.

14:46.351 --> 14:48.119
Jade, what are you doing here?

14:48.119 --> 14:50.291
- [Jade] Chris, I'm pregnant.

14:53.291 --> 14:54.591
- What do you expect me to do?

14:54.591 --> 14:56.494
It's not my responsibility.

14:56.494 --> 14:57.461
You can take care of it.

14:57.461 --> 14:58.996
You guys got a lot of money.

14:58.996 --> 15:00.365
- What?

15:00.365 --> 15:02.167
- I got too much on the
line to deal with this.

15:02.167 --> 15:04.101
Just go, get outta
here, just go.

15:04.101 --> 15:05.669
- [Jade] I have
nowhere else to go.

15:05.669 --> 15:07.139
Wait, please, wait.

15:09.139 --> 15:14.446
Please come back, I have
nowhere else to go, please?

15:14.446 --> 15:17.148
(hitting door lightly)

15:17.148 --> 15:18.450
(crying)

15:18.450 --> 15:20.150
- I'll see you
all Sunday morning

15:20.150 --> 15:22.620
where we'll worship together
and remember, God is good

15:22.620 --> 15:24.722
- All the time.
- All the time,

15:24.722 --> 15:26.256
- [Group] God is good.

15:26.256 --> 15:29.234
(light peaceful music)

15:36.234 --> 15:38.168
- I really did have
a nice night tonight.

15:38.168 --> 15:40.538
Thank you for dinner.

15:40.538 --> 15:43.674
- You know, you and Faith
really mean the world to me.

15:43.674 --> 15:45.643
- We love you, too.

15:45.643 --> 15:47.578
- How have you put up
with me all these years?

15:47.578 --> 15:48.513
