troubling you.

56:31.654 --> 56:35.523
- I just don't understand
what God wants from me.

56:35.523 --> 56:37.726
- I know that feeling well.

56:37.726 --> 56:40.128
Did something happen that
brought these feelings out?

56:40.128 --> 56:41.831
- I recently lost
both my parents

56:41.831 --> 56:44.000
