than a year later,

01:03:25.233 --> 01:03:28.202
I blew out my other knee even
worse than the first time.

01:03:28.202 --> 01:03:31.139
You know, I started
to ask god why?

01:03:31.139 --> 01:03:32.608
Why would he let me work so hard

01:03:32.608 --> 01:03:34.543
to come back from
the first knee injury

01:03:34.543 --> 01:03:36.378
just to let it happen again?

01:03:36.378 --> 01:03:38.280
- I'm so sorry.

01:03:38.280 --> 01:03:43.085
- Thanks, but I knew God
had greater plans for me,

01:03:43.085 --> 01:03:45.987
plans that I was not aware of,

01:03:45.987 --> 01:03:49.423
plans even greater than
playing the game of football.

01:03:49.423 --> 01:03:53.494
