my nephew doing?

01:04:02.003 --> 01:04:03.405
- Man, he's really knocking
the cover off the ball.

01:04:03.405 --> 01:04:05.340
- Well, how's his
fielding going?

01:04:05.340 --> 01:04:06.942
- He's having a great year.

01:04:06.942 --> 01:04:08.251
- [Rev] That's good.

01:04:16.251 --> 01:04:19.655
- You have a wonderful day.
