- [Faith] Aunt Pam,
I'm so glad you came.

01:07:59.740 --> 01:08:01.643
- Me too, sweetie,
you did a great job.

01:08:01.643 --> 01:08:03.577
- [Faith] Thank you.

01:08:03.577 --> 01:08:04.411
- Hey Faith, wait up.

01:08:04.411 --> 01:08:05.746
- Hey, Michael.

01:08:05.746 --> 01:08:07.481
- I wanna introduce
you to my parents.

01:08:07.481 --> 01:08:10.452
- Hi Faith, I'm Rachel and
